title: Jenn-Air® Refrigerators: Discover the Details | Jenn-Air
description:
Jenn-Air® built-in refrigerators have exterior design options that blend in beautifully or become a striking focal point in your kitchen. And with the Obsidian interior, every model showcases an industry-exclusive feature that adds an elegant look to a luxury home. Additional features like multi-point LED lighting and improve sound performance allow these built-in refrigerators to create a sensorial experience that has no equal. You'll find inspiring details, whether you're planning on buying a refrigerator or simply want to learn more about the Jenn-Air brand. 

Abt is a proud authorized retailer of Jenn-Air Refrigerators. Shop for Jenn-Air Refrigerators, as well as the full line of Jenn-Air Appliances at Abt!
